- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and emotion detection from text.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a framework using machine learning techniques to predict fine-grained dimensional emotions.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training a model to predict emotions.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a less likely category, but the paper does touch upon the societal implications of emotion detection from text.
- cs.SD (Sound) is a less likely category, but the paper's focus on emotion detection could potentially be applied to audio data as well.
